RUN:

$sudo make install

Example:
$lmcipher 1337 plain.txt

and/or

$lmcipher 1337 plain.txt.hid

Now about partyvan:

$partyvan [off] [dir]

Example:

$partyvan .
Will encrypt all the files in the current directory recursivelly.

$partyvan off .
Will decrypt all the files in the current directory recursivelly.

$partyvan ~/dir
Will encrypt all the files in that directory.

$partyvan off ~/dir

